            intrusion prevention systems (IPSs), sandboxing, and other security
            point products to their old-school firewalls. But this siloed approach
            just leads to complexity and an even greater potential for breach.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-success" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("PackageTypesView","PackageTypes")'">Go Offers &raquo; </a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>GlobalProtect</h2>
        <p>
            Provide unmatched threat prevention
            capabilities to protect users against
            evasive application traffic, phishing, credential theft,
