            protection of our Next-generation Firewall to your mobile users.
            NuGet is a free Visual Studio extension that makes it easy to add, remove, and update libraries and tools in Visual Studio projects.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-success" onclick="location.href='@Url.Action("SecurityHireTypes","Home")'">Go Offers &raquo; </a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        <h2>Threat Prevention</h2>
        <p>
